OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy morning with,
OL,6,Fespecially across northern and western
OL,7,Fparts, outbreaks of mostly light rain.
OL,8,FThe rain edges away north around
OL,9,Fmidday with the afternoon then largely
OL,10,Fdry with some long sunny spells
OL,11,Fdeveloping. Fresh southwesterly winds
OL,12,Feasing.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA fine evening with some late
OL,15,Fsunshine and mainly light winds. Cloud
OL,16,Fincreasing from the west overnight
OL,17,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,18,Facross western and central areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
