OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSome early brightness in
OL,6,Fsoutheast, but generally a cloudy
OL,7,Fmorning with outbreaks of occasionally
OL,8,Fheavy rain. During the afternoon the
OL,9,Frain turns more showery and perhaps
OL,10,Fthundery.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunny
OL,13,Fspells and showers Sunday, but
OL,14,Fcloudier later. Cloud and outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain on Monday clear to sunny spells
OL,16,Fand showers. Rather cloudy Tuesday
OL,17,Fwith occasionally heavy rain or
OL,18,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
